Everyone knows

00:03:40.280 --> 00:03:42.599
Bian Shui is at the border of three Southeast Asian countries.

00:03:42.719 --> 00:03:45.520
Chinese people don't have much influence here.

00:03:46.039 --> 00:03:48.080
We neighbors

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:50.560
rely on doing a bit of small handicraft work

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:52.680
just to barely scrape by.

00:03:53.479 --> 00:03:54.879
Old Buddha is right about that.

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:58.120
Auntie Wang gets up at five every day to do embroidery.

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:58.840
Old Pang,

00:03:58.919 --> 00:04:00.039
at his age,

00:04:00.039 --> 00:04:01.400
