00:04:28.279 --> 00:04:29.040
Manager Bai,

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:29.759
you tell us.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:30.720
Alright, alright.

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:32.920
The Chinese Association

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:34.920
