00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:42.480
sell all their products.

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:42.959
That's good.

00:04:42.959 --> 00:04:44.399
This is a good thing!

00:04:44.399 --> 00:04:45.439
A good thing.

