00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:07.399
Now,

00:05:07.639 --> 00:05:08.720
every month,

00:05:08.839 --> 00:05:10.160
you only need to pay ten percent.

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:11.199
Ten percent?

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:12.480
Ten percent.

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:16.959
Ten percent.

00:05:16.959 --> 00:05:17.959
Ten percent is fine too.

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:19.800
As long as we can sell all our goods,

00:05:19.839 --> 00:05:22.040
