00:05:54.120 --> 00:05:55.120
Our Old Street,

00:05:55.319 --> 00:05:57.120
it's Zhao Fengsheng who's causing trouble.

00:05:57.480 --> 00:05:58.879
At worst, we just kick him out. Darn it.

