00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:56.279
Why don't you have a nice chat

00:06:56.399 --> 00:06:57.959
with our Manager Bai?

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:02.480
Tomorrow,

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:04.399
tomorrow you two should go see a movie,

00:07:04.480 --> 00:07:05.120
